Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here at the Fumizuki Academy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a school festival called the{\i0}\N{\i1}"Refreshing Festival" will soon be held.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:45.05,Main,,0,0,0,,"The school festival is around the corner!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:49.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since this school is using special systems,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:52.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}such as the Summoner Test War,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:55.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there's a huge turnout for{\i0}\N{\i1}the school festival every year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:58.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to live up to people's expectations, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:01.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the students rouse themselves{\i0}\N{\i1}and strive to prepare for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:10.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Around that time, Year 2, Class F was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:16.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Come back... Come back to life, Muttsulini!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:18.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...trying resuscitation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the red threads of fate are tangled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:26.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll tie them into a bow{\i0}\N{\i1}even if I need to do it by force{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:34.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't untie that exciting{\i0}\N{\i1}future of ours! It's a promise, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm training my heart muscles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:42.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll accomplish my love splendidly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:47.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(LOVE) The data from (CRY) a failed love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:52.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(TRASH) can no longer be{\i0}\N{\i1}of any help, it's so obvious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:57.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(SO) Whenever I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:02.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like it's my first love... Am I cute?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:08.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We talk like we understand,{\i0}\N{\i1}noisily, noisily, noisily!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:10.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My friends are chatty{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:18.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what everyone wants to{\i0}\N{\i1}know is their own score in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:22.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh? An average score is out of{\i0}\N{\i1}question? My Darling is a cut above{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:26.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In practice, it's a terrible unrequited love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:30.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's start leveling up. High! High! High!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:32.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the red threads of fate are tangled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll tie them into a bow{\i0}\N{\i1}even if I need to do it by force{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:37.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thumping heart panic!{\i0}\N{\i1}A sudden development with you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:40.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't look that way! Come with me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm training my heart muscles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surprisingly, today again,{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm tough and blindly in love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:49.17,MainTop,,0,0,0,,BAKA and TEST\N-Summon the Beasts-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:50.17,Main,,0,0,0,,"Day 1"\N"Me, Maids, and a New Start"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A few days ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:57.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the students started preparing{\i0}\N{\i1}for the Refreshing Festival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:01.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Around that time, Year 2, Class F was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:06.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...playing baseball.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.27,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll take you on, Sugawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the next pitch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Throw a curve ball...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:28.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...at the batter's head...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's a foul play!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't hold back! Throw with all your might!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You brats! Why are you slacking off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh shoot! It's Iron Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii! You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you always have something against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no question that the\Nringleader is Yuuji, the class rep, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm? Throw a forkball...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...at Iron Man's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...crotch?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop messing around!\NBesides, I'm the one who'll get scolded!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:05.25,Main,,0,0,0,,All of you, just go back to your classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:09.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the only class that hasn't\Ndecided what to do for the school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,So... we're gonna decide\Nwhat to do for the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Raise your hand if there's\Nsomething you wanna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, Muttsulini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,A photo studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:24.10,Main,,0,0,0,,What kind of photos are\Nyou planning on displaying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:24.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:26.68,Main,,0,0,0,,A secret...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,In the room, we'll display\Nprecious photos that offer a peek
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.81,Main,,0,0,0,,into a mysterious world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.77,Main,,0,0,0,,At least it's a suggestion.\NWrite it down on the blackboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Photo studio...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:45.66,Main,,0,0,0,,A secret... A... A secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:49.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Peek... I-In the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:51.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:52.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... Himeji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:56.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... How about a wedding café?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:05:01.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Similar to maid cafés,\Nwaitresses will wear a wedding dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:04.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that might be cute. Sounds like\Nit's something girls would really like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Guys might like it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:09.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Marriage is the graveyard of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:11.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa, write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:15.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Wedding... Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:17.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:19.53,Main,,0,0,0,,How about a Chinese-style café?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:22.32,Main,,0,0,0,,To do something different from\Nother classes, we'll serve dim sum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:25.45,Main,,0,0,0,,They say that there's no other\Ngenre as deep as Chinese culture...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,...although it's being overshadowed\Nby European culture these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:30.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa, write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:34.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Chinese style... European...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:38.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Akihisa. Aren't you writing\Nonly those words stuck in your hea--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:42.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You brats! Have you decided\Nwhat you're gonna do in the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:44.72,Main,,0,0,0,,There're three ideas so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:49.64,Main,,0,0,0,,"Photo studio" "Secret peeking room" "Wedding café"\N"Graveyard of life" "Chinese-style café" "European"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should increase the\Namount of remedial classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:06:01.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez, why don't you do\Nthings a little more seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:06.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna make a profit so\Nyou can improve your class equipment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:09.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you mean us buying\Ndesks with the money we make?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! I didn't think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:15.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that allowed, Teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You may be really stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:20.63,Main,,0,0,0,,but I never expected your desks\Nwould go even below the cardboard boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:23.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Although it is a penalty,\Nif it interferes with your studies,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:24.88,Main,,0,0,0,,then we're getting our priorities wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:28.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll negotiate with the principal\Nto give you permission to do so
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:30.89,Main,,0,0,0,,as part of the school events.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,So we won't have to study with a\Ndrawing board and a mat like this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,That will allow me to\Nget the better of my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:44.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Nothing... Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:46.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I-In any case, that\Nsounds interesting, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:49.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay then, I'll take a vote!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:51.08,Main,,0,0,0,,--Splendidly done.\N--Raise your hand for what you wanna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.12,Main,,0,0,0,,"Fumizuki Academy Refreshing Festival"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:00.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, this should do it.\NI hope we'll have a bunch of customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:05.13,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to fail this time,\Nso try very hard, okay, Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? What do you mean by "this time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I was asked not to tell anyone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,...Mizuki may have to change schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:17.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Himeji may have to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:21.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...change schools?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:26.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no... when we still have to{\i0}\N{\i1}make a lot of fun memories...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's the only one who brings{\i0}\N{\i1}a breath of fresh air to Class F!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:31.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's gonna happen if she changes schools?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:34.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone will lose their\Nhope, the class will fall apart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.96,Main,,0,0,0,,and we'll enter a hell\Nwhere violence and looting rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:40.38,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll all have mohawk haircuts,\Njust like in {\i1}Fist of the North Star,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,and spend every day fighting\Nover the single heroine, Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa's having a system meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.85,Main,,0,0,0,,He's bad at dealing with unexpected situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:01.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:05.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you still like me even\Nif I have a mohawk haircut?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:08.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What kind of thought process would lead
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:11.49,Main,,0,0,0,,from Mizuki's changing\Nschools to this kind of reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is Himeji changing schools?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:19.17,Main,,0,0,0,,She said her parents are worried\Nabout her studying in Class F.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:20.33,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:24.67,Main,,0,0,0,,She's among guys with low marks\Nand is in a very bad environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.26,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just natural that they worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,If she changes schools, she can\Nstudy in a normal environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:38.14,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's why she said she\Ncould get the better of her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:41.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. If we buy a full set of decent equipment,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.73,Main,,0,0,0,,she might be able to persuade her father, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:47.24,Main,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, we can't fail, huh, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:49.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:51.99,Main,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:58.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsuchiya made a dish for the\NChinese-style café. Could you guys try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Sesame dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:03.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:05.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's crispy outside and sticky inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:10.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It's good that it's not too sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.22,Main,,0,0,0,,This makes me want to drink some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:13.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go make some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:24.73,Main,,0,0,0,,So this is that good? Maybe I'll try, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:27.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's hard outside and gluey inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:31.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not too sweet or too spicy. It's very...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.03,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Akihisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Muttsulini, did you really\Nmake those sesame dumplings?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:40.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:43.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I made three...\NWhy were there more than three?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:49.51,Main,,0,0,0,,From the symptoms, there's no\Ndoubt that it was what Himeji made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:53.30,Main,,0,0,0,,That was close! It was\NRussian roulette with 50-50 odds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:58.18,Main,,0,0,0,,--Woosh... Grandpa, I'm coming now...\N--He really is a guy with bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:04.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, on the day of the school festival...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:17.66,Main,,0,0,0,,"Chinese-style café"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:28.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Chinese-style café, European!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:30.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone! Please, someone resuscitate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:32.51,Main,,0,0,0,,We've already done this scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa, we don't have enough people.\NCould you help in the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:45.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped. I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:47.19,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Chinese-style café: European"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.40,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome! We're currently asking our\Ncustomers who their favorite waitress is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Please vote on your way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:01.75,Main,,0,0,0,,It now looks like a café more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:06.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're getting many\Ncustomers, too. Looks like it's a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, just how long are you gonna make us wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:09.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:13.26,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the problem with this café?\NAren't you gonna take our orders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:16.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I'll be right there.\NHold on a second, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:19.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! We've been waiting all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:23.98,Main,,0,0,0,,We've got other places we gotta go too.\NDon't make us wait forever, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:26.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry! Hold on a second, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,What's their problem, acting so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:32.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Those Year 3 guys... Troublesome customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously, we're hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:36.45,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Sesame Dumplings: 200 yen" "Sample"\NOh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, those look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,It's hard outside and gluey inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:49.67,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not too sweet or too spicy. It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh shoot! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.88,Main,,0,0,0,,300 joules! Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:58.68,Main,,0,0,0,,300! Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:01.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:09.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Phew, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:10.73,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys seem quite used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm always hovering\Nbetween life and death, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,But what on earth happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:23.62,Main,,0,0,0,,To think that there're\Npeople who'd eat sample food...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell's with the food here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:31.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to kill us?!\NI-It's no laughing matter, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't good. We have to{\i0}\N{\i1}somehow smooth things over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:39.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Congratulations! You're the\Nfirst one to hit the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:40.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Hit the jackpot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:43.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have a gift or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:47.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What? A gift? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Here! Say "ahh"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:51.94,Main,,0,0,0,,No way we can eat that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,You bastard! You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,We're gonna make it so that\Nyou'll have to close this café.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! You ate them on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Who's in charg--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm the class rep, Yuuji Sakamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there something you're unsatisfied with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:14.92,Main,,0,0,0,,N-Natsukawa was just knocked off his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:18.51,Main,,0,0,0,,That was my special\Nnegotiation skill, "start with a punch."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:20.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:29.14,Main,,0,0,0,,And, this is my special negotiation\Nskill, "follow up with a kick."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:32.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow... Hm? Tsunemura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:37.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Also, I can finish up with\Nmy special negotiation skill,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:39.44,Main,,0,0,0,,"strangle them with a pro-wrestling technique."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.82,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No thanks. That was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:44.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:48.75,Main,,0,0,0,,...this concludes the negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty good lock, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:52.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the Karl Gotch style, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.88,Main,,0,0,0,,"Order" "Food Name -- Amount" "Sesame dumpling -- 2 pieces" "Punch\Nand kick -- 1 each" "German suplex Karl Gotch style -- Complete set"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:03.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It's somehow gotten slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:10.10,Main,,0,0,0,,This is strange. It's lunch time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,If it stays like this, it won't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:15.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome! Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, Stupid Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:22.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Haduki! You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:26.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! This is the long-awaited\Nschool festival! I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:28.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Haduki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:33.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry, since\Nthis is my future husband's café!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:36.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Also, I've already\Ngiven you my first kiss, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:41.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? Why am I on the floor?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsuchiya! Give me some forks.\NFive should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I need some, too, so ten forks, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:55.27,Main,,0,0,0,,We're now starting the inquisition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:57.65,Main,,0,0,0,,At any rate, immediate death penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ow! Ow! Hey! Hear me out, guys!\N--I know you took the trouble to come, but our café is so deserted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:08.41,Main,,0,0,0,,that it even looks like it's run-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,So it's not like we need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:15.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... I wanted to wear a Chinese dress, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:26.38,Main,,0,0,0,,One hundred meat buns, rush order, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:27.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Get them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:30.76,Main,,0,0,0,,This may be because of that rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:33.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:33.60,Main,,0,0,0,,"First School Festival ~Haduki's Story~ Episode 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:36.89,Main,,0,0,0,,On my way here, I got lost, so I asked people,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:40.36,Main,,0,0,0,,"Where is stupidest Big Brother's café?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:43.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Then everyone told me this place right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You're already like a landmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:52.12,Main,,0,0,0,,But they also told me that this\Nplace was filthy so I'd better not go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:54.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,We all cleaned this place together\Nand even decorated it neatly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:01.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Those customers who came\Nearlier didn't seem unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:03.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they were happy with our café.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Except for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:10.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Probably that Toko-Natsu Duo\Nis spreading a bad rumor about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Toko-Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Their names are Tsunemura and Natsukawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:14.81,Main,,0,0,0,,So if we put the first Chinese\Ncharacters in their names together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:15.68,Main,,0,0,0,,it's read Toko-Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:19.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this, we have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:21.23,Main,,0,0,0,,but to find them and negotiate one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Haduki, where'd you hear that rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:26.40,Main,,0,0,0,,At a café where there are\Na lot of pretty big sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll search high and low!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.91,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems like the goal has changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.87,Main,,0,0,0,,"Maid café"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:42.79,Main,,0,0,0,,So this is the café Haduki was talking\Nabout, huh? Nothing seems unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.59,Main,,0,0,0,,It's too soon to judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:52.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, you look pretty, Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:57.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:17:01.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome home. I won't let\Nyou leave tonight, my darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Here is the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:11.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I'll have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,...water, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:13.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Certainly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:14.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What about you, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:17.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouko, what's with this menu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:21.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Today's Special. Honeymoon with a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Lovey-dovey date with a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:25.63,Main,,0,0,0,,A sweet kiss with a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:28.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Supplies are limited, so please order soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Fat chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:32.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This place is neat and nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:36.60,Main,,0,0,0,,The Chinese-style café by Year 2,\NClass F that we went to earlier was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:37.81,Main,,0,0,0,,What a difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:40.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Their café is filthy and has a weird smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Their waitresses are ugly. On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.40,Main,,0,0,0,,they named a Chinese-style café, "European."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Are they stupid or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Those bastards!\NThey're telling nothing but lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.40,Main,,0,0,0,,One of those is true, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let them get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on. If we attack them here, our\Nbad reputation will spread even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Use your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Then what're we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:02.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouko, let us borrow your maid costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:15.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:17.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Not you, a maid costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:19.97,Main,,0,0,0,,And, I meant let us borrow\Nit if you have an extra one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:22.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go bring one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't make it so obvious\Nthat you're disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:26.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji, what're we gonna\Ndo with the maid costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Obviously, we're gonna ask Hideyoshi for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:32.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I see, that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:33.90,Main,,0,0,0,,"Changing clothes"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.95,Main,,0,0,0,,How's this? Does this look womanly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:41.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa... Well done, Hideyoshi.\NThat looks pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm very good at this kind of makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,E-Even a bra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:48.21,Main,,0,0,0,,If you aren't prepared perfectly,\Nyou can't get into the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:49.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Normally, even underwear is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:50.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.51,Main,,0,0,0,,"Maid café"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously, I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:57.47,Main,,0,0,0,,why a person would go to\Nthat filthy Chinese-style café!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,After all, it's Class F. It can't be any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:08.48,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you want, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:11.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're quite a cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's the matter? Did you fall in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:17.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Shoot! It wasn't far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:23.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You are a guy from Class F...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Eek! This guy is peeking up my skirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! H-Hold on a...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:37.26,Main,,0,0,0,,To think that you act so\Nshamelessly in public... You slimeball!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:39.64,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?! We're the victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:42.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You rubbed the\Nwaitress's breasts, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:44.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! This guy is a perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:48.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What? I can't get it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:52.07,Main,,0,0,0,,See? He's rubbing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:54.19,Main,,0,0,0,,That's totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:59.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsk! Things are looking bad for us.\NWe're getting out of here, Natsukawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:03.70,Main,,0,0,0,,"Haunted House"\N"Entrance"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm... They're made well,\Nbut fakes are fakes, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:13.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's something scarier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Those bastards! They won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:20.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this, we'll do\Nwhatever it takes to make them pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.14,Main,,0,0,0,,What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:24.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I have an idea. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:30.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I must've had a dream since\NI was really hoping for scary stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:34.36,Main,,0,0,0,,But if I hope for pretty stuff instead, I bet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:42.66,Main,,0,0,0,,H-How pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:43.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got my sweet honey, Yoshii, in my heart!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:51.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But her unearthly beauty is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:55.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! It means that I'm denying{\i0}\N{\i1}my feelings towards Yoshii...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:58.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shoot! I didn't ask her name and class!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:00.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I've got Yoshii...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I go after her now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:04.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I've got Yoshii...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:07.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:09.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Please do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:12.69,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Chinese-style café: European"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:14.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:20.82,Main,,0,0,0,,We're getting more customers, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:23.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki and Sakamoto might've pulled it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll help you out a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsk! We let them get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What're we gonna do, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,If they spread bad rumors\Nagain somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:42.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Muttsulini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:44.97,Main,,0,0,0,,We've got a problem.\NOur waitress got kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:49.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:53.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey. You really went and did it earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,We're having your cute\Nwaitress play with us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Your sales must be coming down\Nby now without your poster girl, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:04.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Give Himeji and Minami back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:07.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh-oh, you should try not to upset me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:11.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We'll have plenty\Nof fun with that waitress of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.42,0:22:17.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Those bastards...! I won't forgive them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.55,0:22:21.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Muttsulini, can you figure out\Nwhere the Toko-Natsu Duo is hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:23.01,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:24.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:26.47,Main,,0,0,0,,"Boys Changing Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:33.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Are those images from the\Nsurveillance cameras within the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.19,0:22:36.56,Main,,0,0,0,,But many of them seem to be\Npositioned at too low an angle for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:38.44,Main,,0,0,0,,These are {\i1}my {\i0}surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:44.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I've set up video monitoring\Nin 32 places within the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:47.20,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like the\NToko-Natsu Duo is in any of those places.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:49.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I've set up audio monitoring in 57 places.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.87,0:22:51.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Switch to audio monitoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:14.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Right? They were pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Serves them right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.90,0:23:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.94,0:23:20.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Where is it coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:23.28,Main,,0,0,0,,PE storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:24.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.58,0:23:31.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:33.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:38.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.18,0:23:48.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:53.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:53.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:55.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:00.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.79,0:24:19.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just wait, Himeji! Minami!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.63,0:24:25.26,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.76,0:24:29.01,Main,,0,0,0,,How did you figure out where we were?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.93,0:24:41.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji! Minami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.19,0:24:43.44,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.44,0:24:45.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Those two are working at the café.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.53,0:24:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi... Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.70,0:24:51.78,Main,,0,0,0,,They forced me to come here\Nand made me play a game with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.78,0:24:54.45,Main,,0,0,0,,So you were having plenty of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.45,0:24:56.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Bummed...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.50,0:25:01.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus, the first day of the{\i0}\N{\i1}Refreshing Festival ended.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.71,0:25:03.25,Main,,0,0,0,,"European Sales List"\N"Amount" "Total"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.42,0:25:05.34,Main,,0,0,0,,How were the sales, Shimada?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.34,0:25:06.55,Main,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.55,0:25:09.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Even after subtracting the cost,\Nwe have enough to buy system desks!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.93,0:25:10.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.68,0:25:13.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.14,0:25:15.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What're these huge sales?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.47,0:25:17.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.43,0:25:22.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Splendid photo collection\Nset A by Muttsulini Trading...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.11,0:25:23.98,Main,,0,0,0,,...500 copies, all sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.98,0:25:26.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Refreshing Festival limited edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.36,0:25:29.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, it means today was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.40,0:25:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Stupid Big Brother, this is\Namazing! I'm happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.57,0:25:36.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Haduki. This is thanks to your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.99,0:25:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,The sales are thanks to our waitresses\Nwith great customer-drawing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.75,0:25:42.04,Main,,0,0,0,,"Results"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.46,0:25:44.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm done with the voting results.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.79,0:25:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Today's most popular waitress is...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.59,0:25:55.06,Main,,0,0,0,,"Aki"\N"I didn't know we had such a cutie"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.77,0:26:02.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not even saying that\NI want to be No. 1, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.19,0:26:06.32,Main,,0,0,0,,This frustration... How should I deal with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.53,0:26:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you, Akihisa.\NYou got first place for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.24,0:26:13.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not happy about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.95,0:26:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! Listen, everyone. This is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.24,0:26:18.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.29,0:26:21.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I went to negotiate with the\Nprincipal on your equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.21,0:26:25.34,Main,,0,0,0,,As a special case, she says you can\Nbuy equipment with the café's profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.30,0:26:31.63,Main,,0,0,0,,However... under one condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.63,0:26:33.43,Main,,0,0,0,,On the second day of the Refreshing Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.43,0:26:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,a Summoner Test Tournament will be held.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.43,0:26:37.97,Main,,0,0,0,,If the champion team belongs to your class,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.97,0:26:39.93,Main,,0,0,0,,she'll allow your replacement purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.93,0:26:42.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Summoner Test Tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.10,0:26:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a random tournament by\Nselected teams throughout the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.48,0:26:47.98,Main,,0,0,0,,They're all formidable enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.98,0:26:49.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.78,0:26:55.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you wanna do, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.62,0:26:58.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course! We'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.28,0:27:01.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Those who'd like to participate,\Ncome up with teams and register!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.95,0:27:03.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.06,0:27:25.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day after a holiday should be a holiday!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.06,0:27:34.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day before a holiday should also be a holiday!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.61,0:27:41.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want it to end! I want it to keep going!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.16,0:27:45.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to leave my room!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.79,0:27:50.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to believe it! I can't believe it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.42,0:27:56.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hate Monday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.68,0:28:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't get up, it'll be over{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.18,0:28:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't resist this sleepiness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.85,0:28:10.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can stay like this a bit longer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.48,0:28:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm happy in my dreams!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.28,0:28:19.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I got up, the "iitomo"{\i0}\N{\i1}show had just ended, "Oh no..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.82,0:28:24.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dream turns into a horrific reality{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.41,0:28:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this point, even if I struggle,{\i0}\N{\i1}I can't get that time back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.08,0:28:33.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'm going to dive into{\i0}\N{\i1}the world of dreams once again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.21,0:28:40.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus, the dreams of Year 2,{\i0}\N{\i1}Class F carried on to the second day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.72,0:28:45.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And, here's also a man{\i0}\N{\i1}who chases after his dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.72,0:28:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... I wonder who that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.28,0:28:56.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got a good bargain photo today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.45,0:29:00.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.62,0:29:03.83,Main,,0,0,0,,H-How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.83,0:29:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? What're you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.37,0:29:09.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii! No...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.25,0:29:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.21,0:29:16.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
